  "description": "A panoramic nighttime view of a sprawling urban landscape extending to a dark body of water. The city is densely packed with twinkling lights, creating a vast grid of illumination. A prominent bridge structure with lit segments stretches across the water, connecting urban areas. In the distance, a hazy skyline is visible. The foreground features lower-level buildings and streets, also illuminated, though less intensely than the more distant parts of the city. Above the scene, a dark, cloudy sky dominates, with hints of moonlight breaking through. The overall composition emphasizes the scale and density of the metropolitan area.",
